These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, roller, bus, whiteing
City: liverpool, prague, hannover, boston
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, prince, tiparillo, swisher
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, white, light-blue, black
1. the person traveling to prague is the person driving the subway##1
2. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person who likes white##1
3. the tiparillo-smoker is the person traveling to liverpool##1
4. the person driving the whiteing is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
5. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
6. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
7. the person traveling to prague is the person who likes lavender##1
8. the prince-smoker is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
9. the person driving the whiteing is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Transport         | subway  | whiteing  | roller | bus |
| City           | prague | liverpool | boston  | hannover  |
| Cigar   | swisher       | tiparillo      | siglo | prince      |
| Color           | lavender          | white     | light-blue    | black     |

