.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, accountantcher, librarian, accountant
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, hiking, puzzles, cooking
4 different pets are kept: horse, rat, pony, hamster
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, iris, begonia, daisy
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the hamster is the person who growsorchid##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the mechanic##1
4. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
6. the librarian is the owner of the pony##1
7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the accountantcher##1
8. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the mechanic##1
9. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Job      | librarian     | mechanic       | accountantcher | accountant        |
| Hobby          | cooking     | hiking       | puzzles   | dancing   |
| Pet   | pony      | rat       | hamster     | horse    |
| Flower         | begonia | daisy | orchid | iris |

