.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
House: wooden, cape-cod, ranch-style, cottage
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, old-henry, blend, fonseca
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, february, october, january
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, subway, bus, trike
 1. the cottage house is the person driving the trike##1
 2. the ranch-style house is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
 4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 5. the wooden house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
 8. the ranch-style house is on the right of the game-smoker##1
 9. the wooden house is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
10. the ranch-style house is the fonseca-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| House      | cape-cod | wooden       | cottage        | ranch-style        |
| Cigar           | old-henry   | blend | game   | fonseca |
| Birthday   | december     | february    | january | october        |
| Transport           | bus         | van  | trike       | subway         |

