.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, animation, romance, martial-arts
House: tower, colonial, cottage, craftsman
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, juice, fanta, mirinda
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, may, october, february
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the tower house is on the far right##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the tower house is on the right of the colonial house##1
6. the craftsman house is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
7. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1
9. the person who's birthday is in october is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Movie-Genre           | animation   | satire  | martial-arts | romance |
| House   | cottage | craftsman       | colonial       | tower     |
| Beverage   | fanta       | mirinda    | juice     | almond-milk  |
| Birthday           | may     | october | february     | july         |

