.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, tomato, peas, zucchini
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, cooking, filmmaking, rock-climbing
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, subway, motorbike, scooter
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, bellflower, marigold, zinnia
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person eating onion##1
3. the person who growsbellflower is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the train##1
5. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
6. the person who growszinnia is the person driving the motorbike##1
7. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
8. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
9. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person eating peas##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Food           | onion  | peas    | tomato | zucchini |
| Hobby   | filmmaking      | cooking    | photography         | rock-climbing    |
| Transport   | subway   | train     | motorbike          | scooter      |
| Flower         | bellflower | begonia | zinnia      | marigold      |

