.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, montecristo, siglo, swisher
4 different games are played: bridge, snooker, go, whist
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, blues, house, reggae
City: prague, london, rome, nizza
 1. the siglo-smoker is the fan of folk##1
 2. the oliveros-smoker is the fan of blues##1
 3. the person playing bridge is the fan of folk##1
 4. the person traveling to rome is the oliveros-smoker##1
 5. the fan of house is the person playing whist##1
 6. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
 7. the person playing go is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
 8. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of house##1
 9. the person playing go is on the far left##1
10. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Cigar          | oliveros  | swisher | siglo     | montecristo |
| Game           | go  | whist      | bridge | snooker    |
| Music-Genre   | blues | house  | folk    | reggae  |
| City           | rome   | nizza       | prague       | london      |

