.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-7::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, pilot, nurse, teacher
City: boston, prague, hamburg, marseilles
House: townhouse, tower, palace, farmhouse
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, lavender, ivory, brown
 1. the townhouse house is the person traveling to prague##1
 2. the person who likes brown is on the left of the pilot##1
 3. the nurse is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 4. the tower house is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 5. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 7. the townhouse house is the person who likes ivory##1
 8. the engineer is on the far left##1
 9. the engineer is on the left of the pilot##1
10. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Job    | engineer | pilot     | nurse    | teacher |
| City       | boston | hamburg    | marseilles | prague |
| House         | tower   | palace  | farmhouse        | townhouse    |
| Color   | brown   | lavender | pink    | ivory |

