3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
4. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the french##1
5. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
6. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the argentine##1
7. the person traveling to boston is the argentine##1
8. the chinese is the person eating carrot##1
9. the german is the person eating banana##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Food      | cherry      | carrot         | corn        | banana      |
| City           | boston | venice | hannover  | paris  |
| Flower   | orchid    | amaryllis     | daisy | marigold     |
