.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-9::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, green, fuchsia, coral
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, raspberry, avocado, garlic
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, aconite, rose, marigold
4 different games are played: backgammon, mah-jongg, billiard, bridge
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
4. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
6. the person playing bridge is the person who likes coral##1
7. the person playing billiard is the person who growsazalea##1
8. the person eating avocado is on the far left##1
9. the person eating garlic is the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Color         | green | coral | fuchsia | blood-red     |
| Food   | avocado   | garlic       | cabbage       | raspberry  |
| Flower           | marigold    | aconite    | rose       | azalea       |
| Game     | backgammon     | bridge        | mah-jongg   | billiard |

