5. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
8. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far right##1
9. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Pet          | bird | hamster     | rabbit       | chinchilla |
