4 different pets are kept: goldfish, rabbit, dog, turtle
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, bellflower, iris, zinnia
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, train, helicopter, motorbike
 1. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1
 2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
 3. the indonesian is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
 4. the pakistani is the person who growsiris##1
 5. the polish is on the left of the british##1
 6. the indonesian is on the far right##1
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 8. the person who growsiris is the person driving the train##1
 9. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1
10. the owner of the turtle is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4     |
| Nationality      | pakistani | polish     | british          | indonesian |
| Pet   | turtle   | dog       | goldfish     | rabbit   |
| Flower   | iris    | poppy  | bellflower         | zinnia     |
| Transport         | train | scooter | motorbike | helicopter  |

 